Package datamodel

Interface DataModel<T>

Type Parameters:
T - A generic type
All Known Implementing Classes:
TrainingModel
public interface DataModel<T>
An interface that exposes the services for a DataModel that saves counts extracted from training data. The counts extracted are the ones necessary to calculate a TreeAugmentedNayveBayesClassifier, but might be usefull to other types of classifiers
Since:
2020-05-03
Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Marcelo Jacinto, David Souto, Gonçalo Tomás
See Also:
TrainingModel, TreeAugmentedNayveBayes
